Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:21.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身披天馬聖衣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔天際 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.51,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無遲疑的雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泛著淚光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:37.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不含一絲陰翳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱使遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.98,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱使身死戰地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:47.31,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了跨越那障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.98,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們堅定不移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如星辰般閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:52.94,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星座起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:56.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作指引勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那有限的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒不息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們至深的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.04,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現明晰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未知的極限的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:14.26,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友情編織成的神話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:15.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:16.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮字幕組&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已經失去了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都歸功於薩圖恩大人的偉大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡卻還有人妄圖抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糾纏不休的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是從你們身上奪走時間與聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經遠遠無法滿足我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須連你們的命也搭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有帕拉斯與雅典娜 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位女神的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這兩個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真敢口出狂言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會放任這種事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界失去的時間 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我們來取回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我們一定會打倒薩圖恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠感覺到 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強大的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越神明！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被迷惑了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙已經不是昴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是薩圖恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要操之過急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人忌憚的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這種程度的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想違抗神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由余親手了結你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是黃金聖鬥士 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有這種程度而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 薩圖恩的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然 碰不到他一根手指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無比強大的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連星矢都被一擊就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說中創造了宇宙的Ω的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是站起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路和我並肩作戰的你 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是絕對不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論失敗多少次 人類都會重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的話就快醒醒吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 之後會再犯下同樣的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖劍它…這增強的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對Ω之力產生了反應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我了結你的性命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓這令人敬畏的Ω之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這聖劍的力量 結果了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法與覺醒了的薩圖恩大人抗衡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可說不准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真讓人火大呢 你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有必要為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將被薩圖恩大人打倒的夥伴悲傷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你小子會死在他們前頭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你只有速度算是不落人後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鳥座冰河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真以為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒時刻之神薩圖恩大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 若是像她們那種柔弱的神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定真能實現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能取得她們的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就加入到弒神的行列中去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的實力不相上下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去是無法決出勝負的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在發什麼呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅斬痕（Destructive Slash）！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究極排斥（Ultimate Rejection）！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬的猶豫就會喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的聖鬥士也不過如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真讓人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同Ω的力量一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙星矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩圖恩 你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次站起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來打倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們全都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中的拳已經鈍化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的拳？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在薩圖恩的身上看到了昴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是薩圖恩 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雅典娜的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用這Ω的小宇宙打倒他！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說你們做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:10:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω本身是從拯救昴的心意中萌生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠覺醒究極中的究極小宇宙Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以說明你們對昴有多麼重視
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而 這也是無法簡單捨棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧 光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不會再躊躇 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不會再猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要拯救沙織小姐和世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑軟弱無能的人類嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰 都無法打倒身為神明的余
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢、超越神明！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將小宇宙攻破了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是曾反抗過無數神明的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究是一介凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩圖恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星…星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早該說過了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該弒神了 弒神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星雲氣流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我身陷你的小宇宙漩渦之中 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動彈不得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再見到無謂的流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 歐羅巴 你可得給力點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 雅典娜和帕拉斯就交給哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿 腿凍結了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對零度 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零下273度的凍氣已經封住了你的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你小子就是為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才故意吃下我的攻擊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就無法施展你引以為傲的速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了究極排斥的一擊 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子為何還能毫髮無損
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明打中你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出招的那一刻 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就已經將你的拳頭凍結了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻衣…竟然！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以摧毀聖衣為樂的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:15:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今眼見自己的刻衣被毀壞 感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽石星塵！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥怎會在區區聖鬥士面前 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敗下陣來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才的那番話 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原封不動地還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩圖恩的左右手也不過如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 米拉先生 你已經跪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我一個人來終結這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 歐羅巴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和傳聞中的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到星雲氣流竟能有這樣的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我是不會收手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩圖恩大人的世界很快就要實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我豈能在這種地方退卻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星雲風暴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…多麼強大的小宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 星雲…風…暴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經筋疲力盡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經預料到你會使出星雲風暴了 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女座的瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該繼續弒神之路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 傷似乎比想像的要嚴重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下失去意識的雅典娜和帕拉斯的人頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是輕而易舉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽敢…將帕拉斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼強大的小宇宙 你是從哪裡得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使付出生命 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要保護帕拉斯大人到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱使燃盡全部小宇宙 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗盡生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢欺騙帕拉斯大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐羅巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我有個好建議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分給帕拉斯 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 分給帕拉斯大人 一半世界如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會向薩圖恩大人進言的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 泰坦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混賬的鬼話 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聽膩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨星終結！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然也要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力竭了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω的聖鬥士們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧 已經夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不得不戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織小姐 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了世人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與深愛的人進行了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為深愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是珍視之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才終有一刻 必須親手將一切終結啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是珍視之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤入歧途時 就必須將其打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是珍視之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必須將其阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其打倒之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實會背負起沉痛的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士的戰鬥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾俄洛斯 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你那裡繼承的射手座聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得這麼破爛不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的聖衣啊 只要一擊便好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到放出那一擊為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借給我力量吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那被稱作聖鬥士的宿命的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微不足道的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中可以弒神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金的短劍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等這一刻好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始 目標就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我才能放出…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩圖恩！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾回宇宙的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最深處吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可替代的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回這些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們燃燒至頂點的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的戰鬥！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧、Ω的聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎？
